      <p><a href="<%= new_user_session_url %>"  style="color: #1a73e8; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold;">Log In to Your Account</a></p>
      <div style="margin-top: 30px; padding-top: 15px; border-top: 1px solid #ddd; font-size: 14px; color: #777;">
        <p>Best regards,<br>
        The D & H Realtor Services, LLC</p>
        <p>If you did not authorize this account creation or have any concerns, please contact our support team immediately.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
